    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到奥拉山谷，在这款生活模拟游戏中，你将用自己的语言来塑造故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>创造并照顾你的奥拉</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205530/extras/8a4b95c6f6692c63b0e9994bc0b2534b.avif?t=1727998480\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205530/extras_big/8a4b95c6f6692c63b0e9994bc0b2534b.avif?t=1727998480 width=800 height=289 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >奥拉山谷是一款生活模拟游戏，你将照顾名为“奥拉”的游戏人物。你可以自定义你的奥拉，用自己的话为她们编写人物背景，性格特点和小癖好，让这些人物逐渐变得丰满鲜活起来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>用你的语言定义整个故事</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205530/extras/1c1c1522d8daa51e81179212a80d942b.avif?t=1727998480\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205530/extras_big/1c1c1522d8daa51e81179212a80d942b.avif?t=1727998480 width=800 height=313 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过接地气的语言为你的奥拉设定一些生活小目标，你也可以拓展下朋友圈，交个朋友，谈个恋爱，制造一些狗血剧情让大家来吃瓜什么的，总之，不要让贫穷限制了想象力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>打造理想家园</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205530/extras/051434de8d703a5e978fa082b5d782a6.avif?t=1727998480\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205530/extras_big/051434de8d703a5e978fa082b5d782a6.avif?t=1727998480 width=800 height=313 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >装饰定制化你的家，要有自己的风格；不过首先，你的奥拉需要先打工赚钱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>邀请朋友们做邻居</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205530/extras/ad863d44d6fa41d7f612140ad2dfba6c.avif?t=1727998480\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205530/extras_big/ad863d44d6fa41d7f612140ad2dfba6c.avif?t=1727998480 width=800 height=313 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的奥拉住在一个温馨小镇里，那里还住着其他的奥拉。邀请朋友成为你的邻居。加入后，你可以去找小伙伴们玩耍，和他们的奥拉聊天什么的，不在线也没关系。想约人一起去泡吧吗？邀请你朋友的奥拉一起逛夜市吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索建立社群模式</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205530/extras/f4f6316306e92338af6b4649dcbae9ff.avif?t=1727998480\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205530/extras_big/f4f6316306e92338af6b4649dcbae9ff.avif?t=1727998480 width=800 height=313 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《奥拉山谷》支持模组功能，你可以直接从游戏中下载房屋、人物角色，甚至角色扮演的场景。你还可以使用我们的零代码工具制作自己的模组，什么都可能！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >中文版本正在翻译中，你先体验英文版本，就当练习英文。</p>",
